#: ../../library/omv.display.rst:2
msgid ":mod:`display` --- display driver"
msgstr ":mod:`display` --- 显示驱动"

#: ../../library/omv.display.rst:7
msgid ""
"The ``display`` module is used for driving SPI LCDs, 24-bit parallel LCDs, "
"MIPI DSI LCDs, HDMI output, and Display Port output."
msgstr "``display`` 模块用于驱动SPI LCD、24位并行LCD、MIPI DSI "
"LCD、HDIM输出和显示端口输出。"

